Title: Den hvide slavinde
Actors: Gerda Jensen, Viggo Larsen, Gustav Lund
Plot: A young girl reads an ad in the newspaper and enthusiastically shows it to a young man, who cares for her. She leaves on the train; the young man gives her a carrier pigeon. At the end of the journey, she meets with a lady, who takes her to her house. The girl is given an evening dress and taken to a salon filled with bachantians.
